snippet.title: WATCH DOGS LEGION - E3 2019 GAMEPLAY WALKTHROUGH
snippet.description:
Check out the first official Watch Dogs Legion gameplay walkthrough and follow Jimmy's journey as he joins DedSec London. 

From Piccadilly Circus to Camden Market, through to Scotland Yard, find and recruit new operatives into your resistance. 

Because in Watch Dogs Legion, you get to build your resistance from anyone you meet as you hack, infiltrate, and fight to take back a near-future London that is facing its downfall. 

Reclaim your future!    

Out March 6th 2020 on PS4, Xbox One, PC and Stadia

PRE-ORDER NOW AND PLAY UP TO 3 DAYS EARLY

https://watchdogs.com/buy
